reviews.review_msg: Wynnie is a TA who has now become a professor for semesters when the real prof isn't available. She is a power hungry teacher who wants everyone to do the things she wants to. Apart from her saying "alrighty" in an annoying voice every 3 seconds, her organization is very poor and I would not recommend taking a class with her.
Started as a TA and worked her way up. Great Prof!
